### Discussion Forum App project made by Sydygaliev Kumar for a project review on Intro to Programming Course on 10.05.2025.

This app was written using Flask framework on Python and SQLAlchemy.

# To run on a local machine:
1. Head to the main directory - `DISCUSSION FORUM WEB APP\`
2. Activate the virtual environment - `.\venv\Scripts\activate` (Windows), `source venv/bin/activate` (Linux/MacOS)
3. Enter `cd app`
4. Run project using - `flask run`
5. Enter the main page on a browser - `localhost:5000`

# To stop the running app:
1. Press `Ctrl + C`
2. Enter deactivate or close the terminal
